c: 48
v: 11
t: "The Nomads who lagged behind will say to you: \"We were preoccupied with our money and our family, so ask forgiveness for us.\" They say with their tongues what is not in their hearts. Say: \"Who then would possess any power for you against God if He wanted harm to afflict you or if He wanted benefit for you\" No, God is fully Aware of everything you do"